        <updateDate>2011-03-30T14:36:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Representation for Farmers Act - Amends the Environmental Research, Development, and Demonstration Authorization Act of 1978 to modify the provision governing the composition of the membership of the Science Advisory Board to provide for the appointment of up to three Board members based on a recommendation of the Secretary of Agriculture (USDA). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
